headline: CDW (NasdaqGS:CDW) Expands Digital Offerings With Smartsheet Reseller Partnership
summary: CDW (NasdaqGS:CDW) experienced a notable price movement, with shares rising by over 15% in the past month. This uptick coincides with several significant developments. On May 28, CDW announced a strategic reseller partnership with Smartsheet, aimed at streamlining purchasing processes and promoting technology adoption. Additionally, CDW's Q1 earnings showed increased sales and net income, further supporting the stock's performance. Meanwhile, broader market trends, such as strong earnings...
